  <entry>
    <title>Termux服务器搭建</title>
    <link href="/2024/11/13/Termux%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <url>/2024/11/13/Termux%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="为什么想做-Termux服务器搭建？"><a href="#为什么想做-Termux服务器搭建？" class="headerlink" title="为什么想做 Termux服务器搭建？"></a>为什么想做 Termux服务器搭建？</h1><h3 id="答：我找到我多年的手机，狠狠的利用一下"><a href="#答：我找到我多年的手机，狠狠的利用一下" class="headerlink" title="答：我找到我多年的手机，狠狠的利用一下"></a>答：我找到我多年的手机，狠狠的利用一下</h3><h1 id="第一步"><a href="#第一步" class="headerlink" title="第一步"></a>第一步</h1><ol><li>手机下载Termux<br>官网: <a href="https://github.com/termux/termux-app/releases">https://github.com/termux/termux-app/releases</a> </li><li>找到你的安装包，比如我的miui 11就是Android 7.0我就是第一个<br><img src="/" alt="Termux官网"></li><li>安装</li><li>打开Termux APP<br>我的建议是先安装ssh之后在安装其他的东西，如果你没有电脑的话就当我没说，哈哈哈，先配置</li><li>更换清华源：<figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*stable main\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/termux-packages-24 stable main@&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$PREFIX</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>apt/sources.list<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*games stable\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/game-packages-24 games stable@&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$PREFIX</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>apt<span class="hljs-regexp">/sources.list.d/g</span>ame.list<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*science stable\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/science-packages-24 science stable@&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$PREFIX</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>apt<span class="hljs-regexp">/sources.list.d/</span>science.list<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">apt update</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>如果你不想用了<br>官方源:<figure class="highlight q"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs q">Packages.termux.<span class="hljs-built_in">dev</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>下载ssh<figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">pkg <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> openssh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>运行SSH Server<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">sshd</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>设置用户密码(记住)<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">passwd</span> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>手机 IP(记住)<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">ifconfig</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>获取当前用户名(记住)<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">whoami</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>安装身份认证的包<figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">pkg <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> termux-auth<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="第二步"><a href="#第二步" class="headerlink" title="第二步"></a>第二步</h1><ol><li>将sshd设置为 自启服务<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;sshd&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; ~/.bashrc <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>打开ssh<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">sshd</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>打开你的电脑cmd</li><li>输入ssh，看看有没有安装<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">ssh</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>安装ssh电脑：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_27327057/article/details/126882441">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_27327057/article/details/126882441</a></li><li>在你的cmd ssh连接<figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">ssh</span> 你的用户名_你的手机IP -p <span class="hljs-number">8022</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="安装-Linux"><a href="#安装-Linux" class="headerlink" title="安装 Linux"></a>安装 Linux</h1><ol><li>执行如下命令安装基本依赖<figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">pkg <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> proot git python -y<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh">git <span class="hljs-keyword">clone</span> <span class="hljs-title">https</span>://github.com/sqlsec/termux-install-linux<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> termux-install-linux<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs vim"><span class="hljs-keyword">python</span> termux-linux-install.<span class="hljs-keyword">py</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>之后安装你需要的系统</li></ol><h1 id="进入系统"><a href="#进入系统" class="headerlink" title="进入系统"></a>进入系统</h1><ol><li>Ubuntu:<figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs jboss-cli"><span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> ~<span class="hljs-string">/Termux-Linux/Ubuntu</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./start-ubuntu.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>Kali:<figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs jboss-cli"><span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> ~<span class="hljs-string">/Termux-Linux/Kali</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./start-kali.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>Debian:<figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs jboss-cli"><span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> ~<span class="hljs-string">/Termux-Linux/Debian</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./start-debian.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>CentOS:<figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs jboss-cli"><span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> ~<span class="hljs-string">/Termux-Linux/CentOS</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./start-centos.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>Fedora：<figure class="highlight jboss-cli"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs jboss-cli"><span class="hljs-keyword">cd</span> ~<span class="hljs-string">/Termux-Linux/Fedora</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./start-fedora.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>重建缓存：<figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ada">yum clean <span class="hljs-keyword">all</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">yum makecache</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="ok了"><a href="#ok了" class="headerlink" title="ok了"></a>ok了</h1><h1 id="好玩的东西"><a href="#好玩的东西" class="headerlink" title="好玩的东西"></a>好玩的东西</h1><ol><li>在Termux当中查看系统参数？<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">pkg update</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">pkg <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> screenfetch<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">screenfetch</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
